txt.en: Your standing with the Phetekâri grows. You should visit one of their assistants at Telperiën's Gate, Iridír, Jirush, or Urmâkh to claim a well-earned gift.
Reach Kindred tier with the Phetêkari
Visit the Tale-warden Assistant, Mashêm at Telperiën's Gate, or any of the other Phetekâri quartermasters at Iridír, Jirush, or Urmâkh to claim a gift from the Tale-wardens of Umbar.

'I did not expect such engagement from the people of the North. You have proven an invaluable ally and resource to us.

'Please accept one of these gifts from Captain Rothog and speak with Shulêga for any other you may desire. I shall ensure your name is recognized throughout the Phetekâri.

'You are truly a kindred spirit.'
Visit a Tale-warden's assistant at Iridír, Jirush, or Urmâkh
Your standing among the Tale-wardens earns you a gift. Return to one of their members' quartermasters to be rewarded.

'Please accept one of these gifts from Captain Rothog and speak with a quartermaster for any other you may desire. I shall ensure your name is recognized throughout the Phetekâri.\n\n'You are truly a kindred spirit.'
